Packages
cz.ive Application main classes, used to application startup.
cz.ive.evaltree Main group of classes providing evaulation of expressions The expresion is typicaly used not only for one-shot evaluation, but we are often interested in the changes of expression during simulation time.
cz.ive.evaltree.dependentnodes Provides succesors for different types of nodes in evaltree.
cz.ive.evaltree.leaves Classes for different types of leaves in evaltree and for their managing.
cz.ive.evaltree.links Classes for different types of links in evaltree which differs in type of holded object.
cz.ive.evaltree.mos Classes that use Manager of senses to obtain their value
cz.ive.evaltree.operators.fuzzy Provides classes of fuzzy operators used in evaltree for operating among integer expressions.
cz.ive.evaltree.operators.integer Provides classes of integer operators used in evaltree for operating among fuzzy expressions.
cz.ive.evaltree.operators.set Provides classes of set operators used in evaltree for operating among set expressions.
cz.ive.evaltree.relations Provides succesors of relations defining classes used in evaltree - binary and n-nary succesors are avaible.
cz.ive.evaltree.relations.fuzzy Classes for objects holding and evaulating relations among fuzzy objects.
cz.ive.evaltree.relations.integer Classes for objects holding and evaulating relations among integer objects.
cz.ive.evaltree.relations.set Classes for objects holding and evaulating relations among set objects.
cz.ive.evaltree.time Time related classes that use Calendar to obtain their value
cz.ive.evaltree.topology Topology related classes
cz.ive.evaltree.valueholdersimpl Classes implementig different types used in evaltree which are defined by interfaces in the package cz.ive.valueholders.
cz.ive.exception Specialized exceptions used in the IVE application.
cz.ive.genius Provides interfaces and implementation of geniuses and classes for mannaging them and their behaviour.
cz.ive.genius.goaltree Class implementing the Rule Tree node, which compound whole Rule Tree.
cz.ive.gui Classes providing main part of the GUI and painting of application events.
cz.ive.gui.dialog All dialog windows for the Gui.
cz.ive.gui.icon Provides managemet of icons used in the project.
cz.ive.gui.subwindow Classes for different subwindows - main displaing place of application.
cz.ive.gui.table Gui utilities for easier work with the JTable SWING component.
cz.ive.gui.tree Classes for displaing trees showing hiearchical data structure.
cz.ive.iveobject Provides interfaces and classes of main application object and its derivation.
cz.ive.iveobject.attributes Classes providing different types of attributes used by IveObject class.
cz.ive.location Classes providing location management - creating of locations, path finding, object moving.
cz.ive.lod Provides simple class for LOD embodie and classes for LOD mannaging.
cz.ive.logs Provides classes supporting logging in application.
cz.ive.manager Class of main Manager of Senses and supporting classes to manage queries among objects and their actualization.
cz.ive.messaging Base classes for messaging.
cz.ive.ontology Interface defining ontologies and one simple implementation of it.
cz.ive.process Huge group of interfaces and classes for process managemet - supports mainly Goals, Substitutions, Expansions and process control.
cz.ive.sensors Provides different types of sensors which used to filtrate objects.
cz.ive.simulation Classes providing control among application run like Calendar, Scheduler and Interpreter.
cz.ive.simulation.breakpoint Calendar and Log breakpoints and their management.
cz.ive.template Provides interface for basic template and classes for management of templates.
cz.ive.trigger Classes of different triggers for controling specific events while application is running.
cz.ive.util Provides fundamental classes supporting common operation in IVE application.
cz.ive.valueholders General interfaces defining base types used in application.
cz.ive.xmlload Provides classes which supports load of the application working data ("IVE World") from XML file.
cz.ive.xmlload.creators Provides creators used for XML load.
